Start windows 10
Log in and host Diablo 2
 Use alt+tab to return to the desktop
Switch windows user to the account that will disappear 
Log in and join the hosted Diablo 2 relm
 Use alt+tab to return to desktop and switch user accounts back to the host account 
Now simply log out of Diablo 2 
The system will warn you that other users might lose information 
Acknowledge the warning and continue to exit out of Diablo 2
The user account that was left in-game is now gone!
